@node Author "Locating The Author"

Locating The Author
-------------------

If you like this program and would like to register, reward me for my
efforts, or for bug reports, program ideas, or questions, or just to tell
me about where you live.

I can be contacted through INTERNET EMAIL at:

                              dhomas@unb.ca

Or by MAIL at:
                            scott dhomas trenn
                           797 Mitchell Street
                             Fredericton, NB
                             CANADA  E3B 3S8


Registered users may send me $5.00 for the latest release.  I prefer to
send updates through EMail so be sure to send me your EMail address.  If
you do not have EMail access enclose a disk and your full mailing address
with your payment.

Be sure to include the version number you are currently using, and the
name of the program you want, so I do not send you a version you already
have or a program you do not want.  The version number can be found in the
titlebar, at the top of this documentation file, or by typing:

                          Version SampleUtility

at a shell prompt.  It looks similar to     95.Jan.16

When reporting bugs or errors generated when you run SampleUtility,
please include any error messages given by SampleUtility and also the
version number you are using.  This will aid me in tracking down the
problem. Thank-you.

If you have an EMAIL address please include that with your letter.
@endnode
